Simply slide in your go-to craft beer or hard seltzers and secure it in place with the silicone ring. On top of that, it can be easily converted to a tumbler with the spill-resistant silicone sealed slider lid. When using the game changer as a tumbler, you can safely secure the silicone ring on the bottom. Decorate on the game changer 3-in-1 with our default silk screen branding method.

Sandy food storage box
column4:
When its time to bring your snack to work or to store your leftovers, no more plastic wrap! Keep your sandwich, salad and fruit in this eco friendly bamboo storage box with the lid made from 100% bamboo and the base, 60% bamboo fibers. Choose from a selection of colored silicone bands to compliment your logo and choose from laser engraved branding on the bamboo lid or silk-screening on the container.
note:bamboo & bamboo fiber are natural materials, therefore noticeable shade variations and grain patterns may be apparent within orders of the same item. This wireless charging dock is made from 10% wheat husk, has an integrated 1-meter type-c/usb charging cable which provides fast wireless charging up to 15w, and has built-in fod & ntc overheating protection technology. (devices with integrated magnetic features compatible with ec150: iphone 12 and iphone 13 series).

note: smartphone is for reference only not included.

spectech power products have a one year limited warranty from date of purchase.

column4: This 3 pack of non-refillable single meeting eco notebooks is the perfect companion at every seat around the conference table. Made with 100% recycled materials, each ec302 notebook has 48 lined pages and is the ideal choice for a multi-day conference or convention event. Just enough space for notetaking and the ability to organize each day or topic in their own book. Proudly advertise your message and provide a useful outline of the conference schedule in bold full wrap 4cp on the cover of the envelope wrap box. When you are back in the office, reuse the packaging to file your notebooks together for convenient reference and follow-up before the next round of meetings.

Bamboo adult face mask
column4:
The bamboo mask is an eco-friendly, soft, comfortable, reusable and hand washable adult face mask with a flexible nose piece and adjustable ear loops to customize the perfect fit. This 2-ply face mask is made for all-day wear! The outer shell is made from 50% recycled rayon from bamboo and 50% polyester. The inner lining is made from soft 100% cotton.This mask is non-medical grade.

one size fits most.

care instructions: wash before first use. Hand wash only. Do not bleach. Hang dry. Do not dry clean. Do not iron.
  • the cdc recommends wearing a face covering as one way to address the spread of covid-19. The cdc recommends that social distancing, handwashing, and other recommendations be followed even when face coverings are worn. For more information, please visit www.Cdc.Gov

  • this product should not be used by individuals with lung disease, like emphysema or chronic heart disease, in consultation with / and as advised by a primary care physician or other qualified health professional.

  • stop using this product if you notice difficulty breathing while wearing it.

  • this mask does not replace the personal protective equipment such as n95 respirators used in healthcare settings and should not be used in a healthcare setting.

  • if skin irritation occurs, immediately stop using the mask, if irritation persists, consult your primary care provider.

  • the cdc recommends wearing a face covering as one way to address the spread of covid-19. The cdc recommends that social distancing, handwashing, and other recommendations be followed even when face coverings are worn. For more information, please visit www.Cdc.Gov

  • this product should not be used by individuals with lung disease, like emphysema or chronic heart disease, in consultation with / and as advised by a primary care physician or other qualified health professional.

  • stop using this product if you notice difficulty breathing while wearing it.

  • this mask does not replace the personal protective equipment such as n95 respirators used in healthcare settings and should not be used in a healthcare setting.

  • if skin irritation occurs, immediately stop using the mask, if irritation persists, consult your primary care provider.

column4:
Same great quality in exciting new colors!
this soft cover, non-refillable journal is the perfect addition to our best-selling fabrizio collection. With a ribbon bookmark and 160 ivory lined pages, perforated inner margins and pages edged to match the classic fabrizio colors, its perfect for taking notes in meetings or on your travels.
note: the manual finishing process used to complete the major design element of our fabrizio collection may result in variations of alignment and thickness of the lines of the contrasting black edge trim. These slight inconsistencies may be apparent within orders of the same style and color and are considered normal. (journal inner page dimension is 5 7/16" x 8")

Bamboo & spencer & cynthia 3-piece kit
column4:
Social distancing is key to minimizing germ transmission, so gift the tools of safe practice, all neatly packaged in one box!

the ec913 eco-friendly, soft and reusable 2-ply bamboo mask is adjustable for comfortable, all-day wear. When an in-person signature is required, the plastic, push-action hw204 cynthia pen, treated with a registered antimicrobial additive, is the perfect choice to use when single-use pens are not an option. In between outings and in-person interactions, use spencers touch-free soap or gel sanitizer dispenser. This refillable dispenser, with infrared sensor, offers a safe solution to clean your hands without having to touch or contaminate the machine.

kit includes: ec913 bamboo adult face mask hw912 spencer plastic liquid soap/gel sanitizer dispenser hw204 cynthia ballpoint pen p7104 hefty combo crate with crinkle paper.

Bali portable humidifier/scented oil diffuser
column4: The bali plastic portable humidifier has 4 time settings to maximize output, adding comfort to your surroundings. The oil diffuser will relax and reenergize you at the end of a long day, while the multi-color led lights create a calming atmosphere. Powerful enough to use at home or in the office and portable enough to take along on your travels. Simply plug it into the wall using the included ac adapter or use a usb power source. (scented oil not included.)

Steps sport watch/pedometer
column4:
Available in 8 colors, steps silicone sport watch with plastic pedometer is a fun and fashionable accessory to help you stay in shape. Fasten the silicone strap on securely with the chrome finish metal buckle and start walking! Completed your workout for the day? Store the steps in the provided clear plastic carrying case for easy portability until your next stroll. Keep track of your exercise time on the clock and let the step counter, calorie burning calculator and distance counter all report how you are doing. Includes one lr41 button cell batteries (replaceable)
please note that the electromechanical internal structure of the hw104 differs from its electronic/digital counterparts, therefore tracking results between these 2 types of pedometers will vary. Low intensity movements may affect activity tracking on the hw104. It is recommended to use hw104 for moderate- & high-intensity exercises such as brisk walking & jogging. To enhance distance & step tracking, individual height & weight should be set on the hw104 prior to initial use.
this product has a one year warranty on electronic parts from date of purchase.

Raja yoga mat
column4:
After a good yoga session on the raja low lead pvc yoga mat, you may well feel like royalty. Nothing eases the mind and refreshes the body like a good yoga workout. Comfortable for your feet and easy to carry rolled up and secured with its included black harness and strap, this yoga mat will stay firmly on the ground while your spirit soars. An ideal companion to pair with the hatha yoga mat towel.
yoga mat dimension: 65 1/2" x 24" x 1/8"

Hatha yoga mat towel
column4:
Keep your balance when you hit that yoga pose. The hatha yoga mat towel is ideal for any yoga session thanks to its microfiber material. Machine washable/dryable, lightweight, non-slip and absorbent, with its corner tuck pocket, it fits securely to your yoga mat, or you can use it directly on the floor. Conveniently packaged in a breathable, mesh drawstring pouch. An ideal companion to pair with the raja yoga mat.
towel dimension: 72" x 24"

column4:
Whether you are an athlete or a fan in the stands cheering on the team, this lightweight cooling towel will provide a refreshing cool-down.

Simply soak it in cold water, wring it out and the soft, absorbent polyester material will retain its moisture & coolness to provide relief while you run, go for walks or hikes, exercise or battle the heat.

Towel dimension: 12" x 32"

column4:
Cross body comfort, security and convenience. You have it all in eloises neoprene material with an adjustable shoulder strap. Cynthia push-action ballpoint pen with registered antimicrobial additive
column4:
When an in-person signature is required, minimize the transmission of germs by using cynthia, a plastic, push-action pen treated with a registered antimicrobial additive to prevent product degradation.

cynthia offers default 4cp branding and a standard surewrite low lead ink refill and is presented in individual cello wrapping as the perfect choice for service providers and health care workers to use when single-use pens are not an option.

With kiwi scent and small customizable sleeve (0 07 fl oz / 2 ml per packet)
column4:
Personal hand hygiene with no more runny liquids or communal bottles!

this single-use antibacterial cleanser in a refreshing and invigorating kiwi scent, contains less than 1% fragrance and is made from 98% plant and naturally derived ingredients. Its generously measured into 2 ml, easy to manage gel portions; the perfect size to amply cover all hand sizes.

customize to compliment your promotion. Choose from a small sleeve with 1, 2 or 3 packets, or a large sleeve with 2, 4 or 6 packets and then boldly brand your message on the sleeve in a full coverage, 4cp imprint. (default branding is on the exterior sleeve; the interior sleeve imprint is an available option).

each packet has an easy-tear, notched-top strip, so open it up and work this gel smoothly into your hands to help kill harmful bacteria and germs. Even with numerous hand cleansings throughout the day, dont worry about drying out your skin. The addition of moisturizing aloe vera extract will combat dryness to keep your hands hydrated.

made in canada

    highlighted ingredients:
  • - made from 98% plant and naturally derived ingredients.
  • - contains 65% ethyl alcohol (plant based).
  • - contains aloe vera extract to help keep skin hydrated.
  • - health canada & fda approved formulation.


    • formulated without:
  • - sulfate sls
  • - sulfate sles
  • - parabens

with your keys on the chrome split ring of kagi, its easy to carry everywhere with you, providing a protective barrier between your hands, door handles and elevator buttons.

Nori 3-in-1 ballpoint pen/highlighter/stylus
column4: If you're the kind of person who likes to do three things at once, you need a pen that keeps up with you! Meet the nori, the 3-in-1 pen, highlighter, and stylus. Don't miss a beat while you're working; the tip gives you the option to write with the pen or tap away on your tablet with the stylus. Flip it over to use the highlighter. Clip it to your shirt or clipboard, it'll keep up with you! Not to mention: neon is hot! The highlighter colors match the barrels except the black or white barrels have a yellow highlighter.

Nolan 4-in-1 ballpoint pen/stylus/light/phone holder
column4:
Decorate your brand on nolan, one of our most versatile writing instruments, and let this aluminum 4-in-1 take multi-tasking to a new level. Use the rubber tip as a stylus, remove the cap to sign important documents with the german ink refill and while the cap is off, use the rubberized phone stand feature. Need a little extra light to see what you are doing? No problem, use the push action white flashlight.
note: silver cap has a dark contrast laser effect and black cap has a shiny chrome undercoating.

column4: You'll quickly get used to taking the glacio around with you everywhere, simply for its versatility. This is a reliable push-action heavyweight aluminum pen that leaves plenty of room for branding. With a long-lasting surewrite refill, this pen will be hanging around for a good while. Going more digital? That's fine too: flip it and use the capacitive stylus on the other end. How's that for versatile!

Aubrey ballpoint / stylus
column4: Theres nothing dull about the stylish matte finish of aubreys soft metallic colors. Engrave your logo on the large matte silver clip or use the aluminum barrel as the perfect backdrop, with a dark contrast laser effect on the white and silver barrels. The black rubberized grip will ensure you always have a steady hand whether writing with the surewrite refill, or tapping your smart devices with the black rubber stylus at the end of the chrome plunger

column4: Meet the newest edition of krissy! A stylish aluminum twist-action ballpoint with barrels in brushed anodized metallic colors and a shiny chrome clip and tip. Working with krissy has never been easier, both on paper with her german ink refill and tapping on your touch screen devices with her metallic mesh stylus. For maximum branding exposure, laser engrave your message using the full-wrap 360 degree option.

Ophelia ballpoint pen/stylus with backlight
column4:
Ophelia is more than just a pen/stylus, its a light up pen with an illuminated backdrop to proudly show off your logo!
laser engrave ophelias matte metallic silver plastic barrel and with a firm press on the stylus, your branding will be illuminated by an inner light matching the color of the rubberized grip. (clear light with black grip.)
push the side-action button to write with the surewrite low lead refill, or go paperless and tap away using the black rubber stylus. Either way your logo will shine .

Fabrizio wine temperature sensor
column4:
Its more enjoyable to drink wine at the optimum temperature, so use this elegant fabrizio temperature sensor (in classic black and rich brown vinyl), to ensure you make a good bottle of wine, a great experience. The flexible strap fits a variety of bottle shapes and sizes and the lcd display indicates the temperature in celsius. Deboss your logo discreetly on the strap, or take advantage of the optional full coverage deboss area to extend the branding area of your message on the full length of the strap. Note: the sh100 includes a non-rechargeable and non-replaceable battery with a lifespan of 12 months, and it is recommended to remove the sh100 from a bottle when not in use.
note: the manual finishing process used to complete the major design element of our fabrizio collection may result in variations of alignment and thickness of the lines of the contrasting black edge trim.

Donald coasters (set of 4)
column4:
Four times the surface protection, four times the branding surface messaging. These colorful donald coasters are available in classic black and also in blue, red, green, orange and silver! They will fit into any dcor and pair beautifully with many spector items! Give this set of 4, secured in a vinyl flap closure, as a gift for use at home or in the office and the recipient will be grateful for their practicality in protecting surfaces from hot and cold. As these coasters are used over and over, your brand messaging will be admired for years to come.

note: the manual finishing process used to complete the major design element of our donald collection may result in variations of alignment and thickness of the lines. These slight inconsistencies may be apparent within orders of the same style and color and are considered normal.

Fabrizio cooler / 10-piece bbq set
column4: The ideal picnic companion  just add a grill and your favorite bbq meal! This fabrizio cooler zip bag can hold twenty-four 355ml cans or fill its 12.5l capacity with a bottle of your favorite wine and the ingredients for the perfect outdoor feast. With 2 outer zip side pockets for extra storage, the fabrizio cooler bag is easy to transport using the adjustable carrying strap. It includes all of the ss420/410 stainless steel, dishwasher safe bbq tools you need to prepare a gourmet meal outdoors: a spatula, tongs, grill fork, a steak fork and a 8.5" steak knife, a pair of salt & pepper shakers, a bottle opener and a cutting board. It even includes a grill mitt, heat resistant up to 149c / 300f!

column4: Whether youre city or country bound, keep warm and comfy while you travel with this dakota 100% polyester blanket made of 245g of cozy polyester fleece, (blanket size: 47" x 59" -  unfolded). Available in 4 earth-tone colors with matching blanket stitch all around the edge. Grab it by the woven strap handle of the elastic blanket holder and youre good to go! The strap even has an integrated elastic space to keep a standard 600ml reusable bottle (not included). Convenient, warm, and easy to carry - the dakota is a favorite travel blanket.

column4: Picnic in luxe style with this 52 x 47 polyester-blend blanket that comes in your choice of 3 colors. It folds up and ties neatly under the 600d woven flap with hook and loop closure. Its rubberized finish, metal carabiner and built-in flashlight also make it an ideal accessory for hiking and camping. Let the power bank soak up the sun outdoors to optimize solar recharge. To recharge the off-road a little quicker, use the micro-usb/usb cable and plug into a power source.
spectech-power products have a one year warranty on electronic parts from date of purchase.

column4: The traditional journal joins the digital age! This fabrizio zip journal with both wired and wireless charging technology has it all. (journal inner page dimension is 5 1/2" x 8 1/4")

column4:
You wont have to worry when your smart device starts running low on battery power! This metal power bank has a vinyl cover that matches one of our most popular collections the fabrizio. Not only is it a practical and portable companion, it will make combining items into customized gift sets even easier with journals and speakers from the same color story. The cover doubles as a stand to support your smart phone while charging and branding options are available on both the power bank and cover. 2 usb output ports (1a output or 2.1a output) allows you to charge 2 devices at the same time by using both usb ports individually. For your convenience, it also features 4 led lights that indicates the remaining battery power.
spectech-power products have a one year limited warranty on electronic parts from date of purchase

column4: This robust, ul certified power bank lives up to its name. With 4,000 mah, the commander unites power and portability in a modern matte metallic aluminum case. The t139 commander can recharge your electronic device through its single usb 1a output port on the go while attached to your phone with the included silicone smartphone strap. Its led digital battery status display will let you know how much power remains. Your brand will proudly command attention when decorated on both the power bank and the silicone strap!

Ronan wireless optical mouse
column4: The 3 cs of ronans portable optical mouse design: comfortable, contoured and cordless make web navigation effortless. With 2.4ghz wireless technology, the t142 can reliably be operated at a working distance up to 6 meters. Simply connect the usb nano receiver (included) into an available usb port on your laptop or computer, power on the t142 and click away (no extra software pairing required). For high precision projects or high-speed gaming experience, the t142 has got you covered  easily adjust the cursor sensitivity to 800 or 1600dpi by pressing the dpi button located near the scroll wheel. The t142 is ideal for laser touch branding and makes a perfect companion to the ronan t143 wireless charger mousepad. (note: one non-recycled non-rechargeable alkaline aa battery is included in the t142)

Ronan wireless charging mouse pad
column4:
The ronan wood grain vinyl mousepad has an integrated wireless charging dock, built-in ntc overheating protection and fod (foreign object detection) and a kick stand to support your electronic device at an angle while you are working.

Simply plug ronan into your computer with the provided 2 meter long charging cable, rest your phone over the wireless icon on the mousepad and then watch a movie or play your music while working on your computer without worrying that your phone will run out of power. (compatible with phones equipped with wireless charging technology only.)

Fabrizio keyboard mat/dual charging station
column4:
This spector & co. Original fabrizio keyboard mat/charging station brings elegance and functionality to a desktop. Made with our signature fabrizio material, the t145 is a keyboard mat integrated with dual charging capabilities (by wireless mode on the charge dock or by the usb type-c output fast-charging cable not included). With built-in fod and ntc overheating protection technology, use the large surface area for your keyboard, never miss a notification while your device is charging within your fingertips. Included is a 1.5-meter usb type-c/usb type-c charging cable. Note: to efficiently use the fast-charging feature of this product, it is recommended to use the 20w fast charging wall adapter (not included - see spector item t905).

note: smartphone, tablet, computer, keyboard and mouse are for reference only - not included.

spectech power products have a one year limited warranty from date of purchase.

Cooper 2,200mah ul certified power bank(2056)
column4: Lifes full of surprises and the cooper 2,200 mah ul 2056 certified power bank offers you a good one! Slide open the cover of the plastic case to reveal a neatly tucked-in micro-usb/usb charging cable w/integrated 2-in-1 cable (ios & android). Plug the power bank into a usb power source and the green led light will let you know when its fully charged. Unplug it, flip the cable, and use it to power-up your android or ios device.  All set? Return the cable to its little den, close the cover and admire your logo decorated in full coverage 4 color process!

column4: The timeless style of ettas chrome speaker grill stands out boldly against its clear plastic body. The perfect companion for home or office, this wireless speaker with passive subwoofer has a built-in microphone and offers a playback time of 15 hours after only 3 hours of charging. column4: Double the speakers, double the sound! Enjoy ettas stereo sound output from 2 speakers with passive subwoofers that are not even connected to each other by a cord either assembled as one, in a convenient silicone carrying case for easy portability and storage, or as 2 separate sources of audio connected to 2 different audio devices. This compact stereo speaker lets you do far more: use your tf memory card to pop in your favourite tunes!

Response wireless carabiner speaker
column4:
Whether its a pool, the seaside, or a shower, you can add a dash of music without fear of destroying your wireless speaker. You can bring this little, water-resistant carabiner speaker just about anywhere: clip it to your belt or backpack, or pop it in your purse. Play music, pause, skip to the next song or adjust the volume easily while youre on-the-go. Pair it with your phone and go singing (or talking) in the rain, thanks to its built-in microphone. Make it yours by branding its plastic metallic accent cover.
spectech-sound products have a one year limited warranty on electronic parts from date of purchase

column4:
With control buttons to play, pause and skip songs, the nitro blasts your favourite tunes from your playlist, tf/msd card or selected fm radio station in great stereo sound!
Nitro has 2 speakers and a passive subwoofer to give a stereo sound quality, along with a built-in microphone for hands-free calls. The rubberized finish offers the backdrop for a full-coverage branding option to colorfully promote your message and with the included carrying pouch, you can take nitro with you anywhere.

column4: Keep on trend with the sleek volcano wireless technology v4.1 aluminum earbuds. Use the built-in microphone to answer and end your calls, and play/skip/pause songs or change the volume from a touch on the rubberized buttons. Want to pause your music with minimal effort? Simply rest the cord around your neck and magnetize the ear plates together! Want to continue to listen to your favorite tune? Separate the magnetic ear plates and your music will resume playing. Whats more: youll never hassle with cords because volcano is equipped with a rubberized anti-tangle cord! With 2 hours of charge time, the volcano can be enjoyed up to 7 hours of playback time. The t317 also comes with 2 extra silicone ear cups and a handy zip-case.

Zack 2-in-1 charging cable
column4:
You wont want to give zack back! Its retractable usb cable and 2-in-1 plug for android and ios devices makes keeping your charging cables organized a cinch. Flip the top and pull the cables out to charge your smartphone or tablet via a power source and then when you are done, simply unplug the cables and give it a tug to retract the cables back into the rubberized case for easy storage and portability. No more tangled cables or getting your wires crossed.
*cable transfers data between connected devices.
